'''Floor cleaners''' were [[Droid/Legends|droids]] shaped like small boxes, half a [[Meter/Legends|meter]] long and several [[Centimeter/Legends|centimeters]] high. They ran on treads and were equipped with small arms. They usually ran off of a central [[Computer/Legends|computer]], being too small to be efficiently independent.

